title: No. 1 Sentai Gozyuger Anniversary Discussion
overview: Ahead of No. 1 Sentai Gozyuger's premiere, in a conference room somewhere, Gokai Red, Zenkaizer, Kamen Rider Decade, Kamen Rider Legend, and Gozyu Wolf are sitting in a discussion table. They are engaged in a heated debate about whether Gozyuger should be recognized as an anniversary. What will be the outcome?!
